value: Locally in Acacia scrub of interior of s Australia

arid & semi-arid zones, mainly restricted to Acacia woodlands and tall shrublands, esp.mulga, often with emu-bush understorey, or grass;less often in other woodlands eg.Myall, Gidgee;often vegetated sanddunes
